# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, if you're executing a top-level application, you should commit the lockfile.
#   We keep it commented out.
#Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipenv, poetry.lock is generally committed, but can be ignored if desired.
#poetry.lock

